{"tid":2001670,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"差佬打仔 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-05-04T16:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T16:40:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da67a26a599a5360972ad6d75fc50afb0be0c0a7","tid":2001670,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"全文 link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200504/20911586/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200504%2F20911586%2F&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1qpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=be533d1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200504%2F20911586%2F&h=9f384334\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200504/20911586/</a><br />\n<br />\n差佬打仔 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200504/large/1588489039_48d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200504%2Flarge%2F1588489039_48d9.jpg&h=245ed774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上片段<br />\n<br />\n41歲差佬打仔，肯定情操高尚！不同689施政報告中經常「靈童再現」那個五歲小孩，六歲仔是「實體」。差佬老竇飛腳踢仔心口，也是實體家法侍候。男童不但不感恩，還放聲嚎哭，明顯是郭............................<br />\n被釘棺材釘」的導遊被告，一樣忍唔住。六歲男童被指家中擲拖鞋，模式接近郭官大人定性的「文革式極端主義行為」，擲拖升級就是擲磚啦嘛，是「不折不扣的恐怖活動」。<br />\n<br />\n被控虐兒，差佬未驚過。摷返暗角七警的辯辭，差佬大辯，片段有死角，未能證明有冇剪接。連太子831條港鐵CCTV都未必做到庭上證供，這條差佬虐兒實錄，鄭司長下令，放生差佬，唔使西............................<br />\n強調自己是糾正六歲兒子的歷史觀，還原鴉片戰爭的醜惡。追溯差佬的暴戾基因，全是發動鴉片戰爭的英國佬陰招長期培殖，差佬是以英籍教官陶輝為偶像，唔學傳媒老海鮮藤條教仔，學晒放TG打到人骨折的指揮官絕技，在被告欄內的差佬&times;，顯然曾被小學老師殘害，是鴉片戰爭餘毒的確診者，播毒風險低，適宜輕判家居檢疫777天。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"43dff783c32f6cdfaa4c344b1517f617e13d2135","tid":2001670,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"點解你輯錄到一忽忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003ec6b7152f55d95931f626c6c89b1b4626fac8","tid":2001670,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43dff783c32f6cdfaa4c344b1517f617e13d2135","tid":2001670,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"點解你輯錄到一忽忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"想你俾錢入去"},{"pid":"75203f778473ab9b626d19afac716211264d778c","tid":2001670,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"003ec6b7152f55d95931f626c6c89b1b4626fac8","tid":2001670,"uid":36432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43dff783c32f6cdfaa4c344b1517f617e13d2135","tid":2001670,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"點解你輯錄到一忽忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"想你俾錢入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:40:29.000Z","msg":"都起碼cut好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}